`📊 <b>Pipeline Summary</b>

<b>Total Leads:</b> ${total}
<b>Total Deal Value:</b> ${cur(p.totalDealValue)}

<b>📌 Pipeline Stages</b>
${stageLines}

<b>🏆 Win Rate:</b> ${winRate}% (${won} won / ${won + lost} closed)
<b>⭐ Top Performer:</b> ${topRep}
<b>🔗 Top Lead Source:</b> ${topSrc}

${p.dataFooter}`;
